{
  "stem": "20710.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He-- he always felt that the Germans cannot do things like that, because he used to export, you know, this-- you know, the materials for the barrels to-- to Germany.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he felt that the people that couldn't, you know, he was sort of friendly with them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But so they, so he left anyway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they went, he, and my brother, and I think a few other men.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they went till I guess [POLISH], which was close to the Russian border.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they saw what's going on there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and he left his wife and children and this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he turned back, and he came back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said, now, things cannot be as bad as-- as-- as they are, you know, as they talk about.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But so he came back, yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But not too many people run away, no.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But my-- my brother was taken.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was in the army, so he was taken back to-- to Russia, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was in the Russian Army at that time-- no, he was in the Polish-- let's see.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Oh, it's-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] no, that time the Russian took over, so he was in the Russian Army.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So he was-- you know, when they pulled back, he went back with them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But we didn't know about it till the end.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The youngest.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Herman.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Next-- so the German came in, and they took over.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just, it was a terrible thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were going around just, we didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and being that this was a village, you know, this wasn't a big city like Lwow.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had the Germans came in, they took over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- but being the-- the smaller towns or villages, they gave over the-- the-- the power to the Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
